			'''
		DisplayName: Bloodflare Enchantment
	}

	AuricEnchantment: {
		DisplayName: Auric Enchantment
		Tooltip:
			'''
			Surrounds you with a noticeable protective shield (deals 700 damage, knocks back)
			Press [KEY] to launch 4 huge Aurite bombs (700 damage with a splash and paralysis for 10 seconds).
			Cooldown: 30 seconds.
			'''
	}

	ExoEnchantment: {
		Tooltip:
			'''
			Attacks apply the Miracle Blight debuff to enemies.
			Increases damage for all classes by 15%, critical strike by 10%, and attack speed by 10%.
			Increases melee armor penetration by 10 and true melee armor penetration by 20.
			Increases chance to not consume projectiles by 15%
			Decreases mana cost by 15% and increases mana regeneration by 10%.
			Increases the number of minion and turret slots by 2.
			+100 Rogue Stealth
			+15% health regeneration, +10 defense, +10% damage resistance.

			When wearing a full set of Tech Armor, all bonuses from this enchantment are increased by 25%.
			'''
		DisplayName: Exo Enchantment
	}

	ShadowPhaseEnchantment: {
		DisplayName: Shadowspec Enchantment
		Tooltip:
			'''
			Grants the Enraged buff while the accessory is equipped.
			Increases damage, defense, max health, and minion slots by 10%
			Reduces incoming damage by 5%
			Doubles acceleration.
			Call upon the force of heaven to empower your attacks and minions.
			Courage, Enlightenment, Bliss. United in Judgment
			+2 max minions, 15% increased summon damage, and 8% increased damage to all other classes
			+2 HP/s life regen while flight time is partially or fully expanded
			Press Angelic Alliance Blessing to grace yourself with the Divine Bless.png Divine Bless buff for 15 seconds
			While active, an archangel is summoned for every minion you have
			Archangels vaporize foes with heavenly light and each restore 2 HP upon spawning
			Minion attacks inflict Banishing Fire.png Banishing Fire, and you gain a flat 4 HP/s regen
			This effect has a cooldown of 1 minute
			'''
	}

	OuterCosmosArtifact: {
		DisplayName: Force of Outer Cosmos
		Tooltip:
			'''
			The Rogue's attacks leave a trail of fine Meld plasma particles behind them.
			Hits inflict the 'Shadow Entropy' debuff for 5 seconds, which deals massive damage over time but increases the target's damage by 25%.
			Magical and ranged attacks inflict Astral Contagion on enemies, while True Melee attacks gain armor penetration equal to 20% of your defense.
			Any dashes performed ignite nearby enemies with Godslayer Inferno.
			The Rogue's Stealth builds 20% faster, and their maximum rogue stealth is increased by 50.
			The character permanently gains absolute immunity to the 'Godslayer Inferno' debuff, as well as the 'Omniscience' and 'Astral Thrust' buffs, and the effects of the Ego-Crushing trinket.
			Additionally, maximum health is increased by 25% of maximum mana, defense is increased by ~6.6% of maximum mana
			Whip attack size is increased by 15%
			The size of your summoned minions is increased by 50%
			Maximum mana is increased by 50 for each active minion, and the maximum number of tentacles in the Omega Blue armor set is increased by 5.
			Wearing a full Godslayer armor set grants +15 defense, +10% damage, and +10% movement speed.
			'''
	}

	ObscurantismArtifact: {
		DisplayName: Obscurantism Artifact
		Tooltip:
			'''
			While you stand still, your stats change every second: Defense increases by +3 per second (up to +30), but damage decreases by -5% per second (up to -50%). Any movement instantly resets the accumulated bonus.
			Passive: You are constantly aglow with the 'Wet' effect, emit a soft blue light, and significantly improve underwater visibility.
			While staying in water: Increases defense by 10, reduces speed by 10%, activates +1 to maximum number of minions, activates +3 to maximum number of guards (turrets), increases health regeneration by 10%, and reduces damage resistance by 10%.
			All Classes: Increases critical strike chance by 10% and increases knockback for all weapons by 2x.
			Summoner & Whips: Your summoned minions inflict Plague on enemies for 10 seconds, and whip attack size is increased by 10%.
			Ranged & Ammo: Ranged attacks inflict Plague for 10 seconds. Bullet attacks have a 15% chance to cause a shooting star to fall on the enemy (dealing 100 damage). 
			Flamethrowers additionally poison targets with Acidic Poison for 5 seconds. 
			The chance to save ammo increases the lower your ammo count.
			Magic: Increases maximum mana by 100.
			Debuffs: Cursed Fire deals damage twice as fast, and Ichor reduces enemy defenses by half.
			Energy Shield: A visible energy shield has a 5% chance to reflect enemy projectiles.
			Set Bonus: When wearing a full set of Tarragon Armor, attack speed increases for all classes by 10%.
			Buffs: Permanently grants the 'Tarragon Life' buff.
			Taking any damage grants the 'Silva's Immortality' buff for 5 seconds.
			Bees: When you take damage, you release 5 to 10 Plague Bees.
			Plague Explosions: When your health drops below 100, a powerful Plague explosion occurs around you dealing 300 damage to the summoner.
			If your health drops below 20%, another powerful Plague explosion triggers for 200 ranged damage.
			Both explosions share a 30-second cooldown.
			'''
	}

